    {
      "mode": "managed",
      "type": "konnect_api_document",
      "name": "documents",
      "provider": "provider[\"registry.terraform.io/kong/konnect-beta\"]",
      "instances": [
        {
          "index_key": "rami-apiops-demo",
          "schema_version": 0,
          "attributes": {
            "api_id": "0d303fd3-4b5f-44b0-b68c-48ed535e3a46",
            "content": "# Echo API Documentation APIOps Spark\n\n## Overview\nThe Echo API is designed for testing HTTP methods and debugging requests. It's managed through our ApiOps workflow using Terraform and Kong Konnect, ensuring consistency between OpenAPI specifications and gateway configuration.\n\n## Authentication\nThis API requires **API Key authentication**:\n- **Header**: `apiKey: YOUR_API_KEY`\n- **Required**: All endpoints require a valid API key\n- **Rate Limiting**: 100 requests per minute, 1000 per hour\n\n## Base URL\n```\nhttps://274658be22.gateways.konggateway.com\n```\n\n## Available Endpoints\n\n### GET /anything\nReturns comprehensive information about the request, including headers, query parameters, and metadata.\n\n**Authentication Required**: ✅ Yes (API Key)\n\n**Rate Limits**: \n- 100 requests per minute\n- 1000 requests per hour\n\n**Query Parameters**:\n- `test` (optional): Test parameter for demonstration\n\n**Example Request**:\n```bash\ncurl -H \"apiKey: YOUR_API_KEY\" \\\n     \"https://274658be22.gateways.konggateway.com/anything?test=demo\"\n```\n\n### POST /echo\nEchoes back the posted JSON data with a timestamp.\n\n**Authentication Required**: ✅ Yes (API Key)\n\n**Content-Type**: `application/json`\n\n**Example Request**:\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \\\n     -H \"apiKey: YOUR_API_KEY\" \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d '{\"message\": \"Hello World\", \"test\": true}' \\\n     \"https://274658be22.gateways.konggateway.com/echo\"\n```\n\n## ApiOps Workflow\nThis API was generated using our automated ApiOps workflow:\n\n1. **OpenAPI Specification**: Single source of truth with Kong extensions\n2. **deck Processing**: Kong-compliant resource generation\n3. **Terraform Deployment**: Infrastructure as code\n4. **Developer Portal**: Auto-generated documentation and API catalog\n",
            "created_at": "2026-03-31T09:19:44.706Z",
            "id": "5dede43e-bfb4-4765-8c2e-149b008e724c",
            "parent_document_id": null,
            "slug": "echo-api-docs",
            "status": "published",
            "title": "Echo API - Complete Documentation Virgin Australia",
            "updated_at": "2026-03-31T09:19:44.717Z"
          },
          "sensitive_attributes": [],
          "identity_schema_version": 0,
          "dependencies": [
            "konnect_api.apis"
          ]
        }
